responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D22B825C423E5A769EB2289477F172B9", "Then you shall follow the pathway east, beyond the arch, there lies the village of Samia\'s Hope. Once there. You are to seek out and speak to an Ambassador of Samia\'s Hope. They await as does your destiny.")
